title: Liz Cheney’s PAC to Run Ad Against Lake and Finchem, Both Republicans, in Arizona
description: Representative Liz Cheney, Republican of Wyoming, who lost her primary to a Trump-backed challenger, has been focused on trying to keep election deniers out of office.
dc:creator: Annie Karni
media:credit: Kim Raff for The New York Times
media:description: “I don’t know that I’ve ever voted for a Democrat, but if I lived in Arizona, I absolutely would,” Representative Liz Cheney, Republican of Wyoming, says in an ad.
